The Smart Revision Planner is a web application designed to help students prepare effectively for their exams by generating a personalized study schedule. Students can enter their subjects and exam dates, and the app uses spaced repetition algorithms to automatically create an optimized revision plan. It ensures that each subject is revised multiple times at scientifically proven intervals, improving long-term memory retention. Additionally, the app provides reminders and daily study goals, helping students stay consistent, reduce last-minute stress, and make the most of their preparation time.
